# 🏰 Court of Whispers - Project Walkthrough & Achievements

We have completed an incredibly comprehensive series of gameplay, visual, and architectural overhauls! These changes have transformed the game from a basic prototype into a highly polished, modular, and immersive experience. 

Below is the complete walkthrough of the advanced features we have designed, built, and successfully validated.

---

## 📖 Feature 1: Multi-Page Medieval Storybook Popup
We completely replaced the static, single-page full-screen popup with a customized, interactive storybook layout!

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[Daily Event Trigger] --> B[DailyPopup Frame]
    B --> C[Page 1: Story Intro]
    B --> D[Page 2: Objectives]
    C -->|Next Arrow Button| D
    D -->|Prev Arrow Button| C
    B --> E[Elegant Close Button]
```

* **Medieval Gold Frame Visuals**: Integrated a premium medieval-themed gold-framed panel (`BookFrame`) centered beautifully on screen, complete with custom styleboxes and gold border textures.
* **Interactive Multi-Page Navigation**:
  * Added responsive left/right navigation arrows (`<` and `>`) for seamless flipping.
  * Added a dynamic page-counter label (e.g. `Page 1 of 2`, `Page 2 of 2`) that updates instantly.
  * Designed an elegant circular top-right close button (`×`) that dismisses the popup cleanly.
* **Tween-Powered Transitions**: flip clicks trigger a custom `Tween` that performs a smooth, high-speed cross-fade opacity transition on the text and graphics.
* **Robust Dynamic Loading**: Programmed [game_ui.gd](file:///d:/court-of-whispers-godot/scripts/game_ui.gd) to scan and queue arbitrary lists of daily pages (like `popup1.png` and `popup2.png`), ensuring the system handles any number of pages in the future!

