## 🔌 Feature 4: TanStack Port Connection Fix (`8080`)
We resolved dialogue network errors by aligning the client and server configurations.

* **Port Synchronization**: Since the React backend is powered by **TanStack Start**, its dev server boots on port `8080`.
* **Godot Client Update**: Patched the Godot request client inside [http_agent_client.gd](file:///d:/court-of-whispers-godot/scripts/http_agent_client.gd), [game_config.gd](file:///d:/court-of-whispers-godot/scripts/game_config.gd), and [game_config.tres](file:///d:/court-of-whispers-godot/data/game_config.tres) to point dynamically to `http://127.0.0.1:8080`.
* **Result**: Conversations now hook up and load AI dialogues smoothly without a hitch!

